### Grey Wallet API - Test SMS Endpoints (No Authentication Required)
### Use with VS Code REST Client extension or similar tools
### WARNING: These endpoints are for development/testing only

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
@contentType = application/json

### ========================================
### TEST SMS ENDPOINTS (No Auth Required)
### ========================================

### 1. Test SMS Service Health
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/test/sms/health
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

### 2. Test SMS Account Balance
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/test/sms/balance
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

### 3. Test Send SMS OTP
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/test/sms/send-otp
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "phone": "+254726367035",
  "otp": "123456",
  "expiresIn": 300
}

### 4. Test Send SMS OTP with Different Phone Format
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/test/sms/send-otp
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "phone": "0726367035",
  "otp": "654321",
  "expiresIn": 600
}

### 5. Test Send Custom SMS Message
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/test/sms/test-message
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "phone": "+254726367035",
  "message": "This is a test message from Grey Wallet SMS service. Sent at {{$timestamp}}"
}

### 6. Test Send SMS OTP with Invalid Phone (should fail)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/test/sms/send-otp
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "phone": "invalid-phone",
  "otp": "123456"
}

### 7. Test Send SMS OTP with Missing OTP (should fail)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/test/sms/send-otp
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "phone": "+254726367035"
}
